[
  {
    "startTime": 0.333,
    "endTime": 5.605,
    "text": "♪♪♪"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 5.739,
    "endTime": 7.107,
    "text": "Ha ha!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 7.24,
    "endTime": 11.2,
    "text": "Ah, there's nothing more peaceful than a morning swing through the park."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 11.2,
    "endTime": 12.299999999999999,
    "text": "I don't want to play with trucks!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 12.3,
    "endTime": 13.646,
    "text": "Dinosaurs are more fun!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 13.78,
    "endTime": 16.416,
    "text": "Dinosaurs? No way!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 16.549,
    "endTime": 18.451,
    "text": "Ugh, spoke too soon."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 18.585,
    "endTime": 19.819000000000003,
    "text": "Then I don't want to play."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 19.953,
    "endTime": 21.421,
    "text": "Me neither!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 21.554,
    "endTime": 27.099999999999998,
    "text": "You know, it's OK to disagree, but finding a solution that will make both of you happy might be a lot more fun."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 27.2,
    "endTime": 31.798,
    "text": "I learned that the time Spider-Girl and I had a run-in with super-villain hothead, Electro!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 31.931,
    "endTime": 34.300000000000004,
    "text": "[grunts]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 34.434,
    "endTime": 36.302,
    "text": "I love swinging in the sunshine but..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 36.436,
    "endTime": 38.605,
    "text": "Heh heh, it sure is hot."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 38.738,
    "endTime": 39.939,
    "text": "Ice cream break?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 40.1,
    "endTime": 41.508,
    "text": "I was going to say that!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 41.641,
    "endTime": 42.708,
    "text": "Great Spideys think alike."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 42.9,
    "endTime": 44.11,
    "text": "[giggles]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 44.244,
    "endTime": 45.612,
    "text": "What'll it be, my friends?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 45.745,
    "endTime": 48.815,
    "text": "Mmm, how about two chocolate cones?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 48.948,
    "endTime": 49.682,
    "text": "Hold up!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 49.816,
    "endTime": 51.117000000000004,
    "text": "Chocolate?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 51.251,
    "endTime": 55.922,
    "text": "I'm sorry, Spider Man, but simple creamy vanilla is a much better flavor."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 56.1,
    "endTime": 60.56,
    "text": "What? But, everybody knows chocolate is the greatest flavor since... flavor!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 60.693,
    "endTime": 62.162,
    "text": "[zap]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 62.295,
    "endTime": 63.463,
    "text": "Blackout?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 63.596,
    "endTime": 64.8,
    "text": "[door jingles]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 64.8,
    "endTime": 68.201,
    "text": "Hm, nope, this is the only shop on the block without power."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 68.334,
    "endTime": 70.10300000000001,
    "text": "Let's check the electrical box."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 70.236,
    "endTime": 72.105,
    "text": "The electrical panel was blown."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 72.238,
    "endTime": 74.3,
    "text": "That would take a giant power surge."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 74.3,
    "endTime": 77.1,
    "text": "And I'm guessing that surge was no accident!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 77.143,
    "endTime": 78.545,
    "text": "Follow that scorch mark!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 79.579,
    "endTime": 80.3,
    "text": "E?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 80.3,
    "endTime": 81.5,
    "text": "For Electro!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 81.5,
    "endTime": 84.616,
    "text": "That hot-handed super-villain always signs his work!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 84.751,
    "endTime": 85.61800000000001,
    "text": "Let's get him!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 85.752,
    "endTime": 86.886,
    "text": "Whoa! Whoa, whoa."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 87.0,
    "endTime": 89.155,
    "text": "I think we should restore the power here first."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 89.289,
    "endTime": 91.491,
    "text": "Or all the ice-cream in these freezers will melt."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 91.624,
    "endTime": 93.6,
    "text": "That's a lot of disappointed people."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 93.6,
    "endTime": 96.562,
    "text": "But Electro may cut off power to other ice-cream shops."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 96.696,
    "endTime": 98.298,
    "text": "We have to go after him first."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 98.431,
    "endTime": 100.467,
    "text": "But this shop will need their power fixed."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 100.6,
    "endTime": 102.268,
    "text": "Or their ice-cream will melt."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 102.402,
    "endTime": 105.6,
    "text": "Main street ice-cream and downtown ice-cream have lost power too."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 105.6,
    "endTime": 107.74,
    "text": "Since we can't agree, we'd better split up!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 107.874,
    "endTime": 109.8,
    "text": "Mm hm."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 110.343,
    "endTime": 112.378,
    "text": "[zapping]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 112.4,
    "endTime": 113.5,
    "text": "Knew I was right!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 113.5,
    "endTime": 118.151,
    "text": "If I want to find Electro, just follow the scorch marks and popped light bulbs."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 118.284,
    "endTime": 119.619,
    "text": "[grunts]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 119.752,
    "endTime": 122.755,
    "text": "I've checked out two other shops and they've got their power back on."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 122.889,
    "endTime": 125.524,
    "text": "Central city ice-cream is the only one left in the area."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 130.63,
    "endTime": 134.734,
    "text": "Looks like some careless villain left the door open for the sneaky Spidey."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 134.868,
    "endTime": 136.236,
    "text": "[giggles]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 136.369,
    "endTime": 137.77,
    "text": "Ha! Caught you red-handed!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 137.904,
    "endTime": 139.105,
    "text": "You're mine, Electro!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 139.239,
    "endTime": 140.54,
    "text": "[shouts]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 140.673,
    "endTime": 142.442,
    "text": "[grunts]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 142.575,
    "endTime": 145.20999999999998,
    "text": "I see we're back in sync, Spidey."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 145.345,
    "endTime": 147.13,
    "text": "Great Spideys think alike!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 147.147,
    "endTime": 150.11599999999999,
    "text": "Hey, Electro, what have you got against ice-cream anyway?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 150.25,
    "endTime": 152.485,
    "text": "What did such a delicious treat ever do to you?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 152.619,
    "endTime": 153.5,
    "text": "Melt!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 153.5,
    "endTime": 156.5,
    "text": "My electrcial energy always melts them in my hands."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 156.5,
    "endTime": 160.226,
    "text": "And if I can't have creamy delicious ice-cream, no one can!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 160.36,
    "endTime": 161.895,
    "text": "You could have just had a milkshake."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 162.0,
    "endTime": 164.864,
    "text": "Huh? Argh!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 164.998,
    "endTime": 169.33499999999998,
    "text": "Arguing over whose plan to follow, almost cost us all the ice-cream in town."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 169.469,
    "endTime": 173.47299999999998,
    "text": "By splitting up, we came up with a solution that made us both happy and saved the day."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 173.606,
    "endTime": 175.2,
    "text": "Yeah."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 175.208,
    "endTime": 176.4,
    "text": "Let me buy you an ice-cream."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 176.4,
    "endTime": 178.211,
    "text": "What will you have? Chocolate?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 178.344,
    "endTime": 180.813,
    "text": "Hm, nah. I think I'll have strawberry."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 180.947,
    "endTime": 182.282,
    "text": "That's my other favorite flavor."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 182.415,
    "endTime": 184.684,
    "text": "Heh heh, mine too."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 186.0,
    "endTime": 187.72,
    "text": "Beep beep beep beep."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 187.854,
    "endTime": 189.8,
    "text": "[sound effects]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 189.8,
    "endTime": 195.227,
    "text": "Look at that! The construction trucks built a bridge for the dinosaurs to cross. Nice compromise."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 195.361,
    "endTime": 197.863,
    "text": "Rarrr! Thanks, Miss Bulldozer!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 197.997,
    "endTime": 200.9,
    "text": "Vroom! You're welcome, Triceratops."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 201.0,
    "endTime": 205.572,
    "text": "People don't always agree, but finding ways to compromise can make everyone happier."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 205.705,
    "endTime": 207.20000000000002,
    "text": "That's for sure! Rarr!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 207.2,
    "endTime": 209.20899999999997,
    "text": "Gotcha, Spider Man. Vroom!"
  }
]